# Everything the build produces or the host leaves behind. Keeping these out of
# the context makes the build faster and stops a local .env from being copied
# into an image.
node_modules
**/node_modules
dist
**/dist
.next
**/.next
.turbo
**/.turbo
coverage
**/coverage
.venv
**/.venv
__pycache__
**/__pycache__
.git
.env
.env.*
*.log
